original: Ericsson, John Axel, tandläkare, Vänersborg, f. 1/6/08 i Vänersb. av Axel E. o. Hanna Skoogh. G. 36 m. Svea Eleonora Jo’sefson. Barn: John f. 39, Anders 44. ■— Stud:ex. i Vänersb. 29, med. kand. i Upps. 33, tandläk. 35. Praktik i Brålanda 36-42 o. i Vänersb. ■sed. 42.
translated: Ericsson, John Axel, dentist, Vänersborg, born on 1/6/08 in Vänersborg to Axel E. and Hanna Skoogh. Married in 1936 to Svea Eleonora Jo’sefson. Children: John born in 1939, Anders in 1944. Graduated from high school in Vänersborg in 1929, completed a medical bachelor's degree in Uppsala in 1933, and became a dentist in 1935. Practiced in Brålanda from 1936 to 1942 and in Vänersborg since 1942.
